Requirements: Should be on most linux machines 
- perl
- rrdtool
- ifconfig 

### Create the RRDTool Database

Run the createDatabase.sh script to generate the rrdtool database


### Update the Database

Run the updateDatabase.sh to begin capturing data and populating the database.


### Generate the graph

Generate the graph by running the createGraph.sh


### View the results

View the results on the index.html web page.

### Copying

Consider all this code released under the GNU Public Licence, do with it what you will
providing you adhere to the terms of the licence.


Hope this is useful to some folks out there :)

